{"tid":1701983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只要係香港人，行一切可行之事","createTime":"2019-11-09T12:42:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T07:31:58.000Z","uid":138375,"like":43,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0e725b033919d1a1cc1ac5defaff3050f90afef7","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:42:53.000Z","msg":"係添馬默默哋打呢篇嘢，原諒我嘅分神。<br />\n<br />\n相信大家對近日發生咁多嘢，都等緊一個所謂嘅fc<br />\n我唔係衝動撚，不過，問你自己嘅良心<br />\n等嚟有乜意思？<br />\n等完知道咗<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「你會有乜改變？」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n古代打住正義之師嘅旗號同別國開戰永遠唔需要fc<br />\n求鳩其搵個藉口嚟開戰就得<br />\n係咪熟口熟面？<br />\n<br />\n正正係依家藍絲廢老呃自己為正義而戰冇分別<br />\n保家衛國平亂止暴<br />\n如果佢哋贏咗呢場仗，之前發生嘅元朗恐襲，連儂牆斬人事件，都會變成<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正義人士挺出而出守護香港安寧</span></span><br />\n<br />\n到底我哋等緊一個點樣嘅fc？<br />\n「存疑求真」係正確，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係「真」嘅界線要去到幾深入，先會令到你哋有所改變？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n永遠滿足唔到所有人對fc嘅定義<br />\n其實講到口臭<br />\n我哋放唔低心理包袱咁做啫<br />\n大把嘢可以借題發揮<br />\n從第一隻眼開始<br />\n<br />\n去到有學生離世<br />\n<br />\n傳言有人被強姦<br />\n<br />\n萬一真係有發生到，黑警神速拉嗰啲人出嚟認罪，送埋去坐監<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔通我哋又可以同自己講搞掂，收工，就咁算數</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人都拉咗 無謂搞大佢啦？？？<br />\n係我哋逼到黑警交人，階段性勝利！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n發生咗嘅嘢，捉到人，你想要嘅正義旗號就會隨之消失<br />\n而且仲係揸係對家手上，因為係佢哋搵個所謂「罪犯」出嚟祭旗<br />\n係佢哋捉到犯人，係佢哋願意負責任<br />\n<br />\n你接受？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家仲等緊真正嘅fc，定已經麻木咗？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔需要答我你幾嬲點嬲，亦唔想知你心情<br />\n你自己記住當下個感覺就好<br />\n只要係香港人，有同樣感受，行一切可行之事。<br />\n<br />\n到真係有人去報仇，一定人會話你係鬼，我係鬼之類，樓豬冇開過一個post，實係鬼。<br />\n預咗。<br />\nTime will tell. <br />\n<br />\n只要係香港人，有同樣感受，行一切可行之事。<br />\n令之前嘅計劃兌現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">草木皆兵。<br />\n<br />\n一呼百應。</span>"},{"pid":"14ec4c01b19ddac98acffcaa673461a637322b84","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:43:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18e60fcf91525beef3a8b2b79c3a831b308b59d1","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:43:55.000Z","msg":"只要係香港人，有同樣感受，行一切可行之事。<br />\n令之前嘅計劃兌現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">草木皆兵。<br />\n<br />\n一呼百應。</span>"},{"pid":"942cc3815dfdc41156242a02639f73d8e7cfd9d2","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:44:06.000Z","msg":"只要係香港人，有同樣感受，行一切可行之事。<br />\n令之前嘅計劃兌現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">草木皆兵。<br />\n<br />\n一呼百應。</span>"},{"pid":"c429d067dc1ffc7cbd8c6905c229a86ba1fd93d3","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:44:16.000Z","msg":"只要係香港人，有同樣感受，行一切可行之事。<br />\n令之前嘅計劃兌現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">草木皆兵。<br />\n<br />\n一呼百應。</span>"},{"pid":"a1275b04c0c09a486f6430ef81e0542606e90e3d","tid":1701983,"uid":40521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"殺狗復仇一定要<br />\n唔好送頭 學佢哋 要暗殺"},{"pid":"688e0a0ea559b8888924ea7c4cb48b648b05f47e","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:44:44.000Z","msg":"只要係香港人，有同樣感受，行一切可行之事。<br />\n令之前嘅計劃兌現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">草木皆兵。<br />\n<br />\n一呼百應。</span>"},{"pid":"c9ffed87f55982cc8023b5a1b5f262fd1ef8ddc3","tid":1701983,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">幫手Rt + like </span><br />\n<br />\nSenator Scott嘅tweet嚴重唔夠人推，佢係法案好主要嘅推手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=7d3cf92b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRickScott%2Fstatus%2F1192902065783296006&h=b1cbde8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRickScott/status/1192902065783296006</a><br />\n<br />\nSenator Rubio盡心盡力，迫McConnell迫到咁緊都係唔夠多推，希望大家可以幫幫手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOGzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=bceaa7e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1192955446132387846&h=d2de161b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1192955446132387846</a>"},{"pid":"25cf76c9585fb62b342a1d35336a1fcf9b92d87b","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:44:55.000Z","msg":"只要係香港人，有同樣感受，行一切可行之事。<br />\n令之前嘅計劃兌現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">草木皆兵。<br />\n<br />\n一呼百應。</span>"},{"pid":"7e610b9350de517e7a50fc489e3cc842c4feba81","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:45:08.000Z","msg":"只要係香港人，有同樣感受，行一切可行之事。<br />\n令之前嘅計劃兌現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">草木皆兵。<br />\n<br />\n一呼百應。</span>"},{"pid":"82c91ab3129d74fbae45019531d8eaa795d2fcf1","tid":1701983,"uid":59764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:45:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6307ca0900870eed9d2bf0f93a7b1589415b4c03","tid":1701983,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:46:03.000Z","msg":"***眾籌***<br />\n唔好意思，仲係要借個位&amp;幫你推推POST<br />\n<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,