fd18003a4f","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T12:59:30.000Z","msg":"睇完留個名 不推文都得呀<br />\n<br />\n只要係香港人，行一切可行之事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1701983\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1701983</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做你想做嘅 唔需要計劃<br />\n<br />\n草木皆兵。<br />\n<br />\n一呼百應。</span>"},{"pid":"18fa64db0a49127faaf9310b28aa7e67603255d6","tid":1701983,"uid":336462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:00:01.000Z","msg":"Halo 小弟左此分享惡夢一則<br />\n<br />\n有晚夢到我係間房 臥著床上凝視住沒有關上的門縫 然後我伸手暗上門缝 之後門悄悄地自己打開了 過程重複了數次 心裏非常忐忑 當我再次暗上了門縫後 門再次打開 此時突然飄來一束白色光影 眼見兩位我認識的好友穿著白色衣服站在我身旁 伸手扶起我的右手手掌 然後將我的右手兩節手指放入口裏 突然大力咬緊 二人説：記得一定要幫我地爭取成立調立獨立查委員會 還我地公道。<br />\n<br />\n你又願意為公義冒險ma !<br />\n<br />\n@vvovv2019"},{"pid":"2aec6a12a29b7c2a7e25c8ac7e4f127b53467b11","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:02:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"536a7d6066083f72e0804a8d0d25cfa0ed8cc913","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:06:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f349fb2518de450dc08c4ea6426b36716712db31","tid":1701983,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:07:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3a5e62a0b27527619f45a930dd4204d1dce3aa5","tid":1701983,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:08:40.000Z","msg":"望住你打呢篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029e6ae25034578ede763231a5d8b5360aac5ad8","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:09:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"af45954b54fa33f82a7d4049b4e9a322c66770b7","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:13:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0aa14fab2b2059f30c60376cdc3a616b7aa3f259","tid":1701983,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:17:35.000Z","msg":"Exactly<br />\n從來都係靠信念行事"},{"pid":"dc56f047ce95440df45a999dfe93322bf9226053","tid":1701983,"uid":138375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:21:13.000Z","msg":"推多下"}]}